name: Yama Dharmaraja
shortLoreBlurb: Yama Dharmaraja is a deity from Tibet linked to death judge, protector. Mediates with the dead and fate.
overlapsLinks: Anubis (Egyptian), Athena (Greek), Hel (Norse), Karttikeya (Hindu), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Yama (Buddhist)
